### ── 1. Create course (seeds mock tasks, no Mistral needed) ─────────────────
POST http://localhost:8080/play4change/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sustainability Basics",
  "subjectDomain": "sustainability",
  "moduleTitle": "Introduction to Sustainability",
  "moduleObjective": "Understand the core principles of sustainable living",
  "durationDays": 3
}

### ── 2. Get today's task — copy moduleId from response above ─────────────────
### First call: assigns a random task from pool, stores it
### Repeat call: returns the same task (idempotency test)
GET http://localhost:8080/play4change/tasks/daily?moduleId=4d5f3f99-268a-4d1a-a35d-900dab305af6&dayIndex=0
X-User-Id: user1

### ── 3. Different user — gets a different task from the same pool ────────────
GET http://localhost:8080/play4change/tasks/daily?moduleId=PASTE_MODULE_ID&dayIndex=0
X-User-Id: user2

### ── 4. Submit MCQ answer — copy userTaskId from response above ──────────────
### selectedOption 0 = first option shown (after shuffle)
POST http://localhost:8080/play4change/tasks/PASTE_USER_TASK_ID/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user1

{
  "selectedOption": 0
}

### ── 5. Submit TODO_ACTION answer ────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:8080/play4change/tasks/PASTE_USER_TASK_ID/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user1

{
  "textAnswer": "I brought my reusable bag to the supermarket today instead of using plastic bags."
}

### ── Health check ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### ── Prometheus metrics ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus
